Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.13,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,BEBERAPA HARI KEMUDIAN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.61,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,PUSAT KOTA TEMPEST: RIMURU
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:12.75,tanda-5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs100\bord0\shad0\pos(960,370)\c&HC4DAE2&}Evolusi Tempest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:18.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kisah dari masa yang sangat jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dunia ini, hanya ada empat Naga Sejati.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:29.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah satu dari yang pertama\Nmenjalin keturunan dengan gadis manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:35.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naga Sejati itu mengalihkan sebagian besar\Nkekuatannya kepada sang anak,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu mengkristalkan sisa kekuatannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yaitu perwujudan dirinya sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk melahirkan Elemental Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:49.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Kaisar Naga tumbuh tanpa pernah\Nmengenal wajah orang tuanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:53.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}namun di sisinya selalu ada sosok naga kecil,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hadiah dari sang ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia anak baik.\NSiapa namanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:14.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:17.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak punya nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah kepikiran sebuah nama, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:26.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, karena kekuatanku terlalu besar,\Naku belum berani menamainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:27.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tidak punya nama,\Ndia tetaplah temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:44.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari-hari yang hangat\Nseolah akan berlangsung selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}negara adidaya sihir yang tengah\Ndi puncak kejayaannya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengincar kekuasaan Putri Kaisar Naga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menghabisi sang naga kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:14.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Kaisar Naga tenggelam dalam duka\Ndan amarah membara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:21.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketika kesadarannya kembali berkat\Nkekuatan sesosok Raja Iblis dan Ratu Roh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kejayaan negara adidaya sihir itu\Nsudah tinggal kenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Kaisar Naga pun\Nbangkit menjadi Raja Iblis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan mengorbankan ratusan ribu jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:39.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, keajaiban terjadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sang naga kecil hidup kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:47.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kematian yang telah merenggut jiwanya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:52.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat naga kecil itu menjadi\Nmonster jahat tanpa kehendak, Chaos Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah karena dendam atas kematiannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau kesedihan karena telah membuat\Nsang sahabat berduka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seolah ditelan kebencian,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chaos Dragon menghancurkan segalanya\Ntanpa ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:16.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ternyata temanku sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:23.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Kaisar Naga menyegel sang sahabat\Ndengan tangannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:36.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah pencapaian pertama Putri Kaisar Naga\Nyang telah menjadi Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah kisah kuno yang diwariskan\Nturun-temurun di Dinasti Penyihir Sarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, pasti ada jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besar juga.\NJadi, ini Chaos Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elemental Dragon kuno\Nyang pernah disegel Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temannya Milim, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:46.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rimuru, aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:51.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terus menyerap magi di sekitarnya\Ndan pertumbuhannya tidak berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah terlalu besar untuk bisa disegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kontaminasinya sudah parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:01.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlihat mustahil disembuhkan\Nkarena telah dikuasai Keserakahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku tidak sanggup\Nmelenyapkan temanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahsyat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kastelnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shion! Gobta! Kalian selamat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru!\NKami baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan sudah kembali ke lantai atas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetua sedang mengevakuasi semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan panik!\NKalian aman di dalam menara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga bantu evakuasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami yang akan menghalau\Nserangan Chaos Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan pada kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim bisa mengalahkannya dengan mudah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku tidak ingin\Ndia melakukan itu pada temannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada solusinya.\NTapi bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cahaya apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab. Kemungkinan itu adalah\Njiwa Elemental Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, jiwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya dia jadi Chaos Dragon\Nkarena kehilangan jiwanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Tetapi berdasarkan hasil\Nanalisis terhadap wujud aslinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}telah terkonfirmasi keberadaan jiwa,\Nwadahnya, dan tubuh jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jiwa yang tersisa hanya sebagian kecil,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan akibat kontaminasi,\Nsudah bukan jiwa murni yang seharusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dapat dikatakan jiwa aslinya telah lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, sepertinya dia\Nbelum kehilangan sinarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim, tolong serang Chaos Dragon itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Charybdis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bisa menyerang\Nsampai menyisakan intinya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:45.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti aku akan menyelamatkan jiwa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi, dengan tubuh yang sebesar itu,\Nserangannya tidak boleh tanggung!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut akan melenyapkan segalanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah belajar menahan diri, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:03.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanmu sedang berjuang.\NKamu juga harus menunjukkan tekad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku percaya padamu, Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sesumbar,\Npadahal belum ada jaminan berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin besar harapan yang diberikan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin dalam pula keputusasaan kalau gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, temanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantulkan kerlip\Nbintang-bintang itu di matamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Drago Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keduanya seimbang, ini kesempatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya, Raphael!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik. Siap laksanakan, Tuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:50.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berat sekali, sungguh luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Magiku terus berkurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:54.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keserakahan milik Maribel, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai tidak ada energi jahatnya,\Npasti lebih mudah dibersihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:15.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab, individu Yuuki Kagurazaka
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}telah mengalahkan individu Maribel Rozzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barusan banget?\NSerius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, momen yang pas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim! Bisa tingkatkan keluarannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah mengamankan\Ninti Elemental Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pertaruhkan segalanya sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Drago Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang aku sendiri yang minta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tetap aneh keluarannya masih bisa naik\Nsetelah serangan sekuat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh fisik, lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh spiritual, lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dalam tubuh jiwa, terkonfirmasi\Nadanya inti ilahi dan sisa-sisa jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jadinya?\NNanti bisa meledak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku yang mengurus sisanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lahap semuanya, Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, belum selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus menyelamatkan temanmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Jiwa Buatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, di dalam ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:05.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, ada jiwa Elemental Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tidak ada reaksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau jiwanya tidak bersemayam di sana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:16.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ga-Gawat, apa ada solusi lain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa nama dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya paling efektif\Ndengan memanggil namanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:27.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibarat mengetuk pintu hatinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak yang ada di drama-drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:39.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah terlalu lama,\Naku sampai lupa semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:44.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku sudah menyiapkan nama untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kekuatanku ini\Nsangat sulit dikendalikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyawanya bisa terancam kalau kuberi nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, coba panggil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaia! Namamu Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya namamu Gaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:27.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukalah matamu sebelum temanmu menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:47.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena masih telur,\Npertemuan kalian masih tertunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:56.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua pasti berjalan lancar\Nkalau diserahkan padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang melihatmu bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, ayo kita pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rekan-rekan kita pasti khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, perutku juga lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan ini, masalah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:26.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang nanti aku mau minum bir, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya dari awal bilang padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal serangan Amrita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat susah menyembunyikannya\Ndari para anggota.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, yang penting berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:51.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, karena aku juga memercayaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:55.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda ini benar-benar nekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sampai merebut skill orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:03.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kalau soal Keserakahan,\Nskill-nya yang memilihku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku tidak bisa mengalahkan Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu,\Ntujuanku adalah membunuh Maribel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:15.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Supaya aku bisa bergerak bebas\Ntanpa dicurigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:20.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditambah, semua perbuatan jahat\Njadi dibebankan pada Maribel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:23.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pun terbebas dari segala macam tuduhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda memang mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:32.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencana gadis itu kali ini terlalu gegabah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:37.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Raja Iblis Rimuru dibunuh,\NNaga Badai pasti mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:41.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Chaos Dragon dikendalikan,\Nitu akan membuat murka Raja Iblis Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu memaksakan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:45.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa tebak alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlindungan dari Tuhan Luminus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam situasi yang tidak jelas\Nseberapa besar kerugiannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maribel tidak mungkin mengambil\Ntindakan ekstrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:06.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang terpenting, dia dengan tegas berkata,\N"Tidak perlu khawatir soal itu."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:11.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia tahu Negara-Negara Barat\Ndilindungi oleh Tuhan Luminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:15.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, meski Naga Badai\Ndan Raja Iblis Milim mengamuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kerugiannya masih dalam batas\Nyang bisa dipulihkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:27.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tanya, siapa yang dikalahkan\NLaplace di tanah suci Ruberios?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:32.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Iblis Valentine\Nyang menyamar sebagai Paus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:38.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, tapi Raja Iblis Valentine\Nmasih ada di antara Oktagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:42.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, Raja Iblis yang dikalahkan Laplace\Nadalah palsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:49.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemudian, bicara sosok yang melebihi Paus\Nyang bercokol di pusat Gereja Luminus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:54.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuhan sekaligus Raja Iblis,\NLuminus Valentine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:20:00.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih jauh lagi, Blood Shadow di Amrita\Nbisa menggunakan sihir suci.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:06.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, keluarga Rozzo,\Natau setidaknya Granville Rozzo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}punya hubungan dengan Tuhan Luminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Granville...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:16.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantan Pahlawan Gran itu pernah bertarung\Nsebagai musuh bebuyutan Raja Iblis Luminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hubungan mereka tampak cukup mendalam, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, lebih baik kita menjaga jarak\Ndari keluarga Rozzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya kita memindahkan\Nmarkas ke wilayah timur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, tapi sebelum itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan mengajukan pertemuan\Ndengan Granville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:41.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku korban yang dikendalikan Maribel, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:45.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau minta ganti rugi atas kekacauan\Nyang telah diperbuat gadis itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Anda suka mencari perkara, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku pria yang akan\Nmenjadi raja di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:12.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami memutuskan untuk merestorasi\Nreruntuhan Amrita dan kastel Jistave
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sempat menjadi medan perang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:20.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barang-barang kuno di sana akan dipamerkan\Ndi kastel dan dijadikan museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:25.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghubungkan jalur kereta api,\Nmenatanya sebagai tempat wisata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski itu masih rencana jangka panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuuki menjelaskan bahwa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:35.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lantai terbawah tempat area makam berada,\Nruntuh akibat bom bunuh diri Maribel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya, gadis itu berniat menyeretku\Nmati bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya benar-benar menyesakkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:47.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, setidaknya kecurigaanku\Npada Yuuki sudah hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa tenang\Nmenjalin hubungan kerja sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:52.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.\NKecurigaan Anda telah terbukti benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:59.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Individu Yuuki Kagurazaka\Nbertindak atas kesadarannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kenapa baru bilang sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab. Karena pergerakannya mudah dibaca\Ndan masih bisa dimanfaatkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:15.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Raphael sengaja menyembunyikannya\Ndemi kepentinganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sanggup membunuh Maribel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:22.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti mengambil keputusan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Saya memutuskan\Nhal itu perlu dilakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Payah sekali aku ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku tidak bisa diandalkan,\Nkamu jadi perlu mencemaskanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya hanya tidak ingin memberi\Nbeban mental kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:44.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang mendengarnya,\Ntapi tidak boleh begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menerima kenyataan itu\Ndan memutuskannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,\Nlaporkan semuanya tanpa ditutupi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik. Sesuai keinginan Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:02.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun rencana Yuuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan menghancurkan ambisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:07.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya teman-teman,\Ndan juga partner andal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersama Raphael,\Naku bisa melangkah lurus tanpa tersesat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:18.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kan, Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:26.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin hanya perasaanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:30.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi barusan, Raphael sedikit tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:39.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maribel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:56.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi-lagi, kamu merebutnya dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harapan umat manusia... pupus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:09.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Evolusi Tempest".
